        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>Just a quick one today - I'm running between meetings, and haven't got time to write anything more substantive. But there were a few things I wanted to get into your in-boxes, including a small Instagram change that could have a BIG impact.</p><p>Oh, and the link to the web version of this newsletter is back. Thanks folks who read it on the web for their vigorous feedback; I heard that message loud and clear. üò≥ &nbsp;The link is here to stay from now on. Apologies for its temporary disappearance.</p>"
