      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In one fell swoop, Instagram have dealt a fairly serious blow to the network of companies who exist solely to try to turn that single link into multiple ones. And it's a big market. Last year (admittedly, before the tech winter hit), Linktree was ",
